This is a test file for Experiment I in Principle of Compiler.
Experiment purpose: comprehend the method of Lex programming.
Experiment requirement: 
    Edit a LEX input file that makes it a program to count the
characters, words and rows of text files and can report these 
numbers.The word is a sequence of letters and numbers without
any punctuations or spaces.The punctuation and space are not
considered as words.